Operation		 Description
AND		 	 	 Boolean AND operation between a source operand and a destination operand
OR	 	 	 	 Boolean OR operation between a source operand and a destination operand
XOR		 	 	 Boolean exclusive OR operation between a source operand and a destination 
b. 		 operand
BOT		 	 	 Boolean NOT operation on a destination operand
TEST	 	 	 Implied Boolean AND operation between a source and destination operand
B. setting the CPU flags appropriately
BT, BTC, BTR, BTS       Copy bit n from the source operand to the carry flag and complement/reset/set
B.                      the same bit in the destination operand
